Grim Tuesday is a novel written by Garth Nix in 2004, and was first published in the USA by Scholastic Press and in Great Britain by HarperCollins Children's Books. It is the second book in the Keys to the Kingdom series, and it focuses on Arthur Penhaligonâ€™s quest to regain his place as the rightful heir. Grim Tuesday is afflicted with the deadly sin of greed.